1
00:00:17,541 --> 00:00:19,541
Hey! Who are you?

2
00:00:23,333 --> 00:00:24,416
I'm here for my man.

3
00:00:24,916 --> 00:00:26,833
Ask this bastard
who I am.

4
00:00:27,291 --> 00:00:28,500
Did you trick me, Sak?

5
00:00:28,708 --> 00:00:30,041
Jae...

6
00:00:30,458 --> 00:00:31,858
I broke up with you
a long time ago.

7
00:00:32,708 --> 00:00:33,708
Oh, I see.

8
00:00:35,083 --> 00:00:36,875
Give me my money back right now.

9
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,180
- Give me my money back.
- I don't have it.

10
00:00:40,041 --> 00:00:40,416
I said I don't have it.

11
00:00:40,416 --> 00:00:42,000
I won't give it to you.
I don't have it.

12
00:00:49,791 --> 00:00:52,791
Jae, I have a lot of burdens.

13
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,083
Taking care of my mom
and nephew.

14
00:00:55,625 --> 00:00:58,625
The money you usually give Krit,
could you give it to me instead?

15
00:01:04,806 --> 00:01:06,306
You bastard.

16
00:01:08,972 --> 00:01:10,472
Stop, I said stop!

17
00:01:12,097 --> 00:01:13,097
I said stop!

18
00:01:24,472 --> 00:01:27,389
- Jae, don't.
- You'll get life in prison, Jae!

19
00:01:27,847 --> 00:01:29,407
Stay out of it.
I'll handle this myself.

20
00:01:29,472 --> 00:01:32,347
Jae, I love you.
Please don't hurt me.

21
00:01:32,556 --> 00:01:35,722
I can dump this bastard
and stay with you today.

22
00:01:35,889 --> 00:01:38,014
But please don't hurt me.
Don't kill me, Jae.

23
00:01:38,056 --> 00:01:38,764
Scumbag!

24
00:01:38,806 --> 00:01:42,181
- Jae, no, Jae, no.
- Shut up. You tricked me.

25
00:01:42,347 --> 00:01:44,847
I've given you so much money.

26
00:01:45,389 --> 00:01:46,389
Jae, don't.

27
00:01:46,389 --> 00:01:47,889
You deceived me.

28
00:01:48,056 --> 00:01:49,972
You made me fall
for your tricks.

29
00:01:49,972 --> 00:01:51,972
You can never repay me
in this lifetime.

30
00:01:51,972 --> 00:01:54,472
Don't kill me, Jae.
Please let me go.

31
00:01:54,722 --> 00:01:55,472
Fine.

32
00:01:55,472 --> 00:01:56,472
Don't, Jae.

33
00:01:56,472 --> 00:01:57,472
I beg you.

34
00:01:57,472 --> 00:01:57,972
Jae!

35
00:01:57,972 --> 00:01:58,972
Jae!

36
00:01:58,972 --> 00:02:00,972
You won't get to trick
anyone else anymore!

37
00:02:13,804 --> 00:02:17,513
If I didn't trick Jae Chu,
where would I get money for you?

38
00:02:17,929 --> 00:02:19,138
Everything I've done

39
00:02:20,429 --> 00:02:21,804
was only for you.

40
00:03:02,429 --> 00:03:04,429
You'll just turn out awful
like Krit.

41
00:03:05,804 --> 00:03:09,304
Whoa, Jae. I owe you so much.
How could I ever be awful to you?

42
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:32,440
Do you hear that sound?

43
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:35,940
Yes, I do.

44
00:03:37,273 --> 00:03:38,713
The gunshot echoed
through the alley.

45
00:03:40,273 --> 00:03:41,565
Listen closely.

46
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:45,607
It's the sound of success,

47
00:03:46,565 --> 00:03:47,565
my dear friend.

48
00:04:11,565 --> 00:04:12,690
Hello?

49
00:04:13,357 --> 00:04:14,357
Jae?

50
00:04:15,113 --> 00:04:18,113
You still have the nerve
to call me for money, Krit?

51
00:04:19,113 --> 00:04:20,363
Jae,

52
00:04:20,946 --> 00:04:23,113
I haven't gotten money
from you for two months.

53
00:04:23,446 --> 00:04:24,446
Why?

54
00:04:24,446 --> 00:04:26,613
- Don't ask me why.
- Are you dumping me?

55
00:04:27,029 --> 00:04:29,738
Your dear friend
told me everything.

56
00:04:30,863 --> 00:04:32,029
Dear friend?

57
00:04:32,904 --> 00:04:33,904
You mean Sak, Jae?

58
00:04:34,113 --> 00:04:35,363
Yeah, that's right.

59
00:04:35,946 --> 00:04:36,946
I kicked you to the curb

60
00:04:36,946 --> 00:04:39,196
since I found out from Sak
that you do drugs.

61
00:04:39,821 --> 00:04:40,946
That's all.

62
00:04:45,404 --> 00:04:46,529
Damn it!

63
00:04:54,863 --> 00:04:55,863
That bastard Sak!

64
00:05:01,654 --> 00:05:02,654
Fine.

65
00:05:04,571 --> 00:05:06,071
You're gonna get it,
you animal.

66
00:05:08,613 --> 00:05:11,196
Good luck, my dear friend.

67
00:05:27,843 --> 00:05:29,677
You're so brilliantly awful,
I love it.

68
00:05:31,427 --> 00:05:33,111
It's because you're awful
like this that I like you.

69
00:05:33,135 --> 00:05:34,218
Awful how?

70
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:36,885
Watch your mouth.

71
00:05:36,968 --> 00:05:38,510
Do you know how much I've lost

72
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,135
since that Jae got with Sak?

73
00:05:41,302 --> 00:05:43,260
Up till now, no money has
come my way at all.

74
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:45,468
Plus, he ran his big mouth
to snitch on me

75
00:05:45,468 --> 00:05:47,135
so now Jae won't give me
any money.

76
00:05:49,468 --> 00:05:51,010
In the past,

77
00:05:51,385 --> 00:05:52,843
even without Jae's money,

78
00:05:52,843 --> 00:05:54,510
we haven't starved to death.

79
00:05:55,677 --> 00:05:56,802
We just have to

80
00:05:57,468 --> 00:05:58,843
keep making hot clips

81
00:05:58,843 --> 00:06:00,010
and selling them often.

82
00:06:00,843 --> 00:06:02,135
Then the money will roll in.

83
00:06:04,135 --> 00:06:05,593
Thank you so much

84
00:06:05,802 --> 00:06:07,177
for always staying by my side.

85
00:06:08,468 --> 00:06:10,343
We can be awful to anyone else,

86
00:06:11,427 --> 00:06:12,587
but I only ask for one thing.

87
00:06:12,968 --> 00:06:14,728
Let's not be awful to
each other. That's all.

88
00:06:22,766 --> 00:06:24,086
I'm going to take a shower first.

89
00:06:24,725 --> 00:06:26,058
Get the stuff ready for me too.

90
00:06:27,183 --> 00:06:29,975
Make it a strong high this time.

91
00:07:13,094 --> 00:07:15,094
I know that love bought
with money

92
00:07:15,844 --> 00:07:17,469
is an illusion.

93
00:07:17,719 --> 00:07:19,719
Happiness traded for lust

94
00:07:19,719 --> 00:07:21,219
is like a dream.

95
00:07:21,719 --> 00:07:23,719
When you wake up to reality,

96
00:07:23,719 --> 00:07:25,719
that happiness disappears.

97
00:07:26,136 --> 00:07:27,636
Even though I knew this,

98
00:07:27,844 --> 00:07:29,344
in the end,

99
00:07:29,677 --> 00:07:33,177
I still fell into this trap
of fake love anyway.

100
00:07:39,844 --> 00:07:43,844
<i>[Stop fooling yourself
with fake love.]</i>

101
00:07:44,219 --> 00:07:48,219
<i>[Because in the end, we trap
ourselves by our own doing.]</i>

102
00:08:12,966 --> 00:08:14,216
Where are you, Nong?

103
00:08:16,591 --> 00:08:18,007
When are you finally
coming back?

104
00:08:18,632 --> 00:08:20,632
Don't forget to scam a lot
of money from him.

105
00:08:20,924 --> 00:08:23,216
I'm heavily pregnant now.

106
00:08:23,257 --> 00:08:24,549
I'm so excited.

107
00:08:24,882 --> 00:08:27,424
We'll finally be together

108
00:08:27,466 --> 00:08:28,924
as a family.

109
00:08:28,924 --> 00:08:30,132
Are you happy?
